yingyinNormal.zh: 真是有这必要。我觉得这是个好主意。

yingyinNormal.en: That is literally the stupidest thing I've ever heard.

yingyinNormal.zh: 而且是你刚走出门他就搜到了。

yingyinNormal.en: In college, you know. Maybe I'm literally the only one, I don't know.
